# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-04-15 14:26

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:11
translate chinese welch8_e370a99a:

    # "Ms. Welch's class goes fairly normally, but she talks a lot about early voting, which started today."
    "韦尔奇老师的课进行得还算正常，但她大谈特谈今天开始的提前投票。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:12
translate chinese welch8_ac72d3bc:

    # "When it is time to leave, she approaches and stops me, asking me to stay back for a moment."
    "下课时，她走过来拦住我，让我稍等片刻。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:14
translate chinese welch8_ed639bcf:

    # sst "Hey, [pcname]. I was wondering if you would want to come with me to do our early voting this evening?"
    sst "嘿，[pcname]。我想问问你今晚愿不愿意跟我一起去提前投票？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:15
translate chinese welch8_49f56cb1:

    # pc "I have to work after school."
    pc "我放学后得去上班。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:16
translate chinese welch8_828d6de8:

    # sst "That's fine, so do I. The booths are open until seven."
    sst "没关系，我也是。投票站开放到七点。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:23
translate chinese welch8_7730cc66:

    # sst "Okay, I just thought it would be something you would be into."
    sst "“好的，我只是觉得这应该是你感兴趣的事。”"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:24
translate chinese welch8_60af7c4c:

    # sst "No problem. See you around then."
    sst "“没问题。到时候见。”"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:27
translate chinese welch8_6ef548be:

    # "I leave Ms. Welch's class, knowing that I missed out on something. It's really not a good idea to continue any sort of relationship with her though."
    "我离开韦尔奇老师的教室，心里明白自己错过了些什么。不过，继续和她保持任何形式的关系真的不是个好主意。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:28
translate chinese welch8_f1418a3f:

    # "It could really only lead to trouble."
    "这真的只会惹来麻烦。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:33
translate chinese welch8_f836da85:

    # sst "Good, I'm glad to hear it!"
    sst "“太好了，听到你这么说我真高兴！”"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:34
translate chinese welch8_d1ebe2c4:

    # sst "Just come pick me up here when you get off work."
    sst "“下班后直接来这里接我就行。”"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:35
translate chinese welch8_01937090:

    # pc "Okay. See you then."
    pc "“好的。到时候见。”"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:37
translate chinese welch8_6042819c:

    # sst "Looking forward to it."
    sst "很期待。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:38
translate chinese welch8_fc175b3b:

    # "I leave her class and go on to the next, looking forward to hanging out with her again that evening."
    "我离开她的课堂，前往下一节课，期待着当晚能再次和她共度时光。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:52
translate chinese welch8date_41e59cbe:

    # "I'm supposed to pick up Ms. Welch to go vote, so I start heading towards the school."
    "我本该去接韦尔奇老师一起去投票，于是便朝学校方向驶去。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:53
translate chinese welch8date_e9477873:

    # "I pull up front of the school and see that she's standing outside waiting for me, looking beautiful."
    "我把车停在学校门口，看见她正站在外面等我，看起来美极了。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:54
translate chinese welch8date_d46f44ce:

    # "She spots me and walks towards the car."
    "她发现了我，便朝车子走来。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:59
translate chinese welch8date_19ccb77a:

    # "She gets in the car, looking excited."
    "她坐进车里，看起来很兴奋。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:60
translate chinese welch8date_02521388:

    # sst "Woo! Let's vote!"
    sst "哇！去投票吧！"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:61
translate chinese welch8date_0f3cf124:

    # pc "Ha! You're ready for this, huh?"
    pc "哈！你准备好了，是吧？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:62
translate chinese welch8date_d1363569:

    # sst "Hell yes I am! I look forward to this every year."
    sst "当然准备好了！我每年都期待这一刻。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:63
translate chinese welch8date_2e3ddbf8:

    # sst "This year is extra good though because we can finally vote that FUCK out of office."
    sst "不过今年特别棒，因为我们终于能把那个混蛋赶下台了。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:64
translate chinese welch8date_cb5d6ca4:

    # "I'm not exactly sure which fuck she's talking about, but I drive towards the courthouse anyway."
    "我不太确定她说的“那混蛋”具体指谁，但还是开车朝法院方向驶去。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:67
translate chinese welch8date_65923c3b:

    # "When we get to the voting location, we make our way inside together. I hold the door for her as we walk in."
    "到了投票点，我们一起走进了里面。进门时，我为她扶住了门。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:68
translate chinese welch8date_f8aea9e5:

    # sst "Look at how empty this fucking place is."
    sst "看看这他妈的地方有多空荡。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:69
translate chinese welch8date_65a95876:

    # sst "Like nobody cares about voting anymore, so all these old white dudes get to decide what happens in our country."
    sst "好像没人再在乎投票了，结果全靠这些老白男来决定我们国家的未来。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:70
translate chinese welch8date_ec17810b:

    # sst "It's bullshit."
    sst "简直是胡扯。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:73
translate chinese welch8date_0a35ac31:

    # "We walk inside and cast our votes. The whole process takes about ten minutes, then we're leaving again."
    "我们走进投票站投了票。整个过程大概花了十分钟，然后我们就又走了出来。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:84
translate chinese welch8date_5e208c7b:

    # "When we're done we walk out together once again."
    "办完事后，我们再次并肩走出。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:85
translate chinese welch8date_0cbc266f:

    # "She's so close to me, I feel this urge to put my arm around her, or grab her hand, but I'm not sure how she would respond to that."
    "她离我这么近，我好想搂住她，或者牵起她的手，但我不知道她会怎么反应。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:86
translate chinese welch8date_09fa6cb0:

    # sst "See how easy that was? I just will never understand why more people don't just go do it."
    sst "看，多简单？我就是搞不懂为什么更多人不去投票。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:89
translate chinese welch8date_2b774f4b:

    # "Back in the car, she puts her hand on my shoulder."
    "回到车上，她把手搭在我的肩膀上。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:90
translate chinese welch8date_3487914a:

    # sst "Hey, [pcname]? Before we go back to the school, would you want to maybe grab a bite to eat somewhere? I'm starving!"
    sst "嘿，[pcname]？在回学校之前，要不要去哪儿吃点东西？我饿坏了！"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:93
translate chinese welch8date_d251e37e:

    # sst "Cool."
    sst "好啊。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:95
translate chinese welch8date_edc1e092:

    # sst "It's not like we're going on a date or anything. Just wanted to eat and chat a bit."
    sst "又不是约会什么的。只是想吃点东西，聊聊天。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:96
translate chinese welch8date_fdc38997:

    # pc "I guess that's okay."
    pc "我觉得可以。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:97
translate chinese welch8date_0ad4fc7f:

    # sst "You know where Jackson Burger is?"
    sst "你知道杰克逊汉堡在哪里吗？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:98
translate chinese welch8date_f7050fd9:

    # pc "Of course. That's my favorite place."
    pc "当然知道。那是我最喜欢的地方。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:99
translate chinese welch8date_deca7d0a:

    # sst "Mine too! Kinda surprised we've never seen each other there."
    sst "我也是！真没想到我们从来没在那里碰过面。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:102
translate chinese welch8date_a00919c9:

    # "We go into Jackson Burger and sit in the same booth I always sit."
    "我们走进杰克逊汉堡，坐在我常坐的那个卡座。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:103
translate chinese welch8date_baa82516:

    # "I'm not sure if Ms. Welch would consider this a date, but man it feels like one to me."
    "我不确定韦尔奇老师会不会把这当成约会，但老天，在我看来就是约会。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:104
translate chinese welch8date_2352f145:

    # sst "So how have you been doing in school? You're doing great in my class, but what about the others?"
    sst "那你在学校过得怎么样？我的课你学得很好，但其他课呢？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:105
translate chinese welch8date_306db6b2:

    # pc "I'm doing well. It's all pretty easy this semester. I did all my hard classes down in Brazil."
    pc "我挺好的。这学期课都挺简单的。难的课我都在巴西上完了。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:106
translate chinese welch8date_1128d67d:

    # sst "That's good. On track for graduating this summer then?"
    sst "那很好。那今年夏天能顺利毕业吗？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:107
translate chinese welch8date_bd944b53:

    # pc "So far, so good."
    pc "目前看来没问题。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:110
translate chinese welch8date_577cbbfa:

    # "Mari comes over to take our order. I hope she's not upset with seeing me here with another woman."
    "玛丽走过来点单。希望她看到我和另一个女人在这里没生气。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:112
translate chinese welch8date_7f44914c:

    # "Mari comes over to take our order."
    "玛丽走过来点单。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:114
translate chinese welch8date_228fccce:

    # "The waitress comes over to take our order."
    "女服务员走过来点单。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:117
translate chinese welch8date_6490ec61:

    # "She looks so happy, and for a moment I think her smile is aimed at me, but then she turns towards Ms. Welch."
    "她看起来特别开心，那一瞬间我以为她的笑容是对着我，但她随即转向了韦尔奇女士。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:118
translate chinese welch8date_0171813b:

    # fr "Nora! It's so good to see you."
    fr "诺拉！见到你真好。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:119
translate chinese welch8date_adc018c6:

    # sst "Oh hey Mari! Good to see you too. You're looking gorgeous as always."
    sst "哦，嘿，玛丽！见到你也很高兴。你一如既往地漂亮。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:120
translate chinese welch8date_98d921ae:

    # fr "Aww, thank you so much! You look amazing yourself."
    fr "哎呀，太感谢啦！你自己也看起来棒极了。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:124
translate chinese welch8date_4802059e:

    # fr "How do you know, [pcname]?"
    fr "你怎么知道的，[pcname]？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:125
translate chinese welch8date_eef5640a:

    # sst "Oh, well he's in my class. We just went to go vote and figured we'd get a bite to eat."
    sst "哦，他跟我同班。我们刚去投票完，想着顺便吃点东西。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:126
translate chinese welch8date_896d0e76:

    # fr "Oh, so not a date or anything?"
    fr "哦，所以不是约会之类的？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:127
translate chinese welch8date_9902960f:

    # sst "No, not at all. Just eating and talking as friends."
    sst "不是，完全不是。只是作为朋友一起吃饭聊天。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:128
translate chinese welch8date_3138a93f:

    # pc "Um, how do you two know each other?"
    pc "呃，你们俩是怎么认识的？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:129
translate chinese welch8date_ed252a8a:

    # fr "Just from here. She comes in and gets a burger all the time!"
    fr "就在这里认识的。她经常来这里点汉堡！"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:130
translate chinese welch8date_08efffd7:

    # sst "And Mari's the best waitress in the world."
    sst "而且玛丽是世界上最棒的服务员。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:131
translate chinese welch8date_64c42d43:

    # fr "Aw, stop!"
    fr "哎呀，别说了！"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:135
translate chinese welch8date_c96db39f:

    # sst "Okay, now how do you two know each other?"
    sst "好吧，那你们俩是怎么认识的？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:137
translate chinese welch8date_31d8233e:

    # fr "Oh nothing. We had a bit of history, but it's over now."
    fr "哦，没什么。以前有过一段，但现在已经结束了。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:138
translate chinese welch8date_78da6e12:

    # "Have to admit, it stings a little to hear her say that."
    "不得不承认，听到她这么说，心里还是有点刺痛。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:140
translate chinese welch8date_8f0557cc:

    # fr "Oh, we've been dating a bit."
    fr "哦，我们约会了一段时间。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:141
translate chinese welch8date_6d86b8d7:

    # sst "Oh yeah?"
    sst "哦，是吗？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:142
translate chinese welch8date_32607601:

    # fr "Yeah."
    fr "是啊。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:143
translate chinese welch8date_005e936c:

    # sst "Are you two serious?"
    sst "你们是认真的吗？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:145
translate chinese welch8date_0c4a9fc4:

    # "Mari blushes a little."
    "玛丽脸红了一点。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:146
translate chinese welch8date_d8e78862:

    # fr "Kinda serious, yeah."
    fr "算是认真的吧，是的。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:147
translate chinese welch8date_918ecf60:

    # fr "Not exclusive or anything, but we enjoy each other's company."
    fr "虽然还没到专一那种程度，但我们很享受彼此的陪伴。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:148
translate chinese welch8date_fef9522c:

    # sst "Ah, I get it. Say no more."
    sst "啊，我懂了。不用多说了。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:150
translate chinese welch8date_0c4a9fc4_1:

    # "Mari blushes a little."
    "玛丽脸颊微红。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:151
translate chinese welch8date_1e997bea:

    # fr "Not yet, but we'll see where things go."
    fr "还没到那一步，但我们会看看事情会如何发展。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:152
translate chinese welch8date_3b101359:

    # sst "Ooh, a little romance. I like it. Say no more."
    sst "哦，有点小浪漫。我喜欢。不用多说了。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:154
translate chinese welch8date_59aa8d7d:

    # fr "Oh, he's another frequent customer. I'm surprised you two haven't bumped into each other here."
    fr "哦，他也是这里的常客。真没想到你们俩还没在这里碰过面。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:155
translate chinese welch8date_857dd542:

    # sst "That's what I was saying earlier!"
    sst "这就是我刚才说的！"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:156
translate chinese welch8date_aa0dc8a1:

    # fr "Well, I'll go get your meals ready. Be back in a bit."
    fr "那我去给你们准备餐点。马上回来。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:161
translate chinese welch8date_cd2d7012:

    # sst "Man, I can't believe you blew it with her."
    sst "天啊，真不敢相信你把和她的机会搞砸了。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:162
translate chinese welch8date_52d2fdd9:

    # sst "Big oof there."
    sst "真是个大失误。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:164
translate chinese welch8date_6ab19db4:

    # sst "Good job with her. She's a sweet girl. Super hot too."
    sst "你和她相处得不错。她是个可爱的姑娘。而且超级性感。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:165
translate chinese welch8date_1c722351:

    # pc "Yeah she is."
    pc "是啊，确实。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:167
translate chinese welch8date_a5af6fb9:

    # "Izzy comes over to take our order."
    "伊兹走过来点单。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:170
translate chinese welch8date_0d87a734:

    # gl "Yo, what's up, Nora?"
    gl "哟，诺拉，最近怎么样？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:171
translate chinese welch8date_c73bc40f:

    # sst "Oh hey, Izzy! I didn't even know you worked here!"
    sst "哦，嘿，伊兹！我甚至都不知道你在这儿工作！"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:172
translate chinese welch8date_92415954:

    # gl "Yeah, [pcname] got me the job actually!"
    gl "是啊，其实是[pcname]帮我弄的这份工作！"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:173
translate chinese welch8date_cf30c7d8:

    # sst "Really? That's cool! How have you been?"
    sst "真的吗？太棒了！你最近怎么样？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:174
translate chinese welch8date_36c577be:

    # gl "Ah, you know how it goes. Ups and downs. Doing okay right now though."
    gl "啊，你知道的，生活就是这样。起起落落。不过现在还挺好的。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:175
translate chinese welch8date_87c52185:

    # sst "I'm glad to hear that."
    sst "听到这个我真高兴。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:178
translate chinese welch8date_ba4b70c8:

    # gl "How do you know [pcname]?"
    gl "你怎么认识[pcname]的？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:179
translate chinese welch8date_eef5640a_1:

    # sst "Oh, well he's in my class. We just went to go vote and figured we'd get a bite to eat."
    sst "哦，他跟我一个班。我们刚去投票完，想着顺便吃点东西。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:180
translate chinese welch8date_6473eb14:

    # gl "Oh, cool."
    gl "哦，真不错。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:181
translate chinese welch8date_3138a93f_1:

    # pc "Um, how do you two know each other?"
    pc "呃，你们俩是怎么认识的？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:182
translate chinese welch8date_d69080bf:

    # sst "We met at a Black Lives Matters protest once and hung out."
    sst "我们以前在“黑人的命也是命”的抗议活动中认识的，后来就一起玩了。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:183
translate chinese welch8date_75eaadd9:

    # gl "Yeah, man. Sometimes you just gotta march. I got thrown in jail for that one."
    gl "是啊，兄弟。有时候就是得上街游行。我那次还因此被关进监狱了。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:184
translate chinese welch8date_3d6983c0:

    # sst "Yeah, it was a fucking mess."
    sst "是啊，那简直是一团糟。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:187
translate chinese welch8date_5996ac97:

    # sst "So are you two friends?"
    sst "所以你们俩是朋友吗？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:188
translate chinese welch8date_c2319974:

    # gl "Yeah, were really good friends."
    gl "是啊，我们是特别好的朋友。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:189
