    sst "真棒！"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:190
translate chinese welch8date_59ad4e63:

    # gl "Well, anyways, it's good seeing you. What do y'all want to eat?"
    gl "不管怎样，见到你真好。你们想吃点什么？"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:191
translate chinese welch8date_f35deb44:

    # "She quickly takes our orders and then rushes to the back."
    "她迅速记下我们的点单，然后匆匆跑向后厨。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:194
translate chinese welch8date_26f19da2:

    # sst "Izzy's a sweet girl."
    sst "伊兹是个可爱的姑娘。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:195
translate chinese welch8date_c417e350:

    # pc "Yeah."
    pc "是啊。"

# game/Scenes/Welch/welch8.rpy:196
